. 
<emphasis box="[810,895,1448,1472]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">adustus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, Beirut: the 
<typeStatus box="[1038,1086,1449,1473]" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">type</typeStatus>
locality of 
<taxonomicName box="[1218,1345,1448,1472]" class="Insecta" family="Drilidae" genus="Drilus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="posticus">
